to this definition">#</a></dt>
<dd><p>Converts spherical polar coordinates to rectangular cartesian
coordinates.</p>
<p>Note that the input angles should be in latitude/longitude or
elevation/azimuthal form.  I.e., the origin is along the equator
rather than at the north pole.</p>
<div class=3D"admonition note">
